# AORTA Rest

Aorta Rest is a simple API allowing tasks to be routed and medical messages to be transferred.

Basic list of the list of services:
 - Task Request (Initiator / Requester of a Task) - Task Management Application
   - Create a Task Request               POST   
   - Delete a Task Request               DELETE
   - Update a Task Request               PUT

 - Patients
   - Create a Patient                    POST
   - Update a Patient                    PUT

 - Patient Admissions
   - Create an Admission                 POST
   - Update an Admission                 PUT

 - Patient Transfers (Pending or Actual)
   - Create a Transfer                   POST
   - Update a Transfer                   PUT

 - Hospital Structure
 
 - Stock
    - Create a Stock Movement Request    POST
    - Update a Stock Movement Request    PUT
 
 - Appointment
   - Create an Appointment               POST
   - Delete an Appointment               DELETE
   - Update an Appointment               PUT 

 - Tasks (
   - Create a Task                       POST   https://aorta:443/api/tasks
   - Delete a Task                       DELETE https://aorta:443/api/tasks/123456
   - Update a Task                       PUT    https://aorta:443/api/tasks/123456


